Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode.4 title
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:23.91,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追 忆 之 笛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 拉紧钢索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 那边太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要随便放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动 到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 放那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 货物都在那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 移动到那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都叫你别用飞的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要切断钢索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你能自己想点办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何处理你的居住权 我们尚无定论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你能暂时在这里生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方太不方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 就 行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 Chamber 附近 方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是账单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,账 单？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求贵官通过劳动补偿对机库造成的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我们赶走海贼的可是雷德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏机库和那是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 雷德刚刚来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们为他免除了逗留期间所消耗的水电费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及将这庞然大物放在船上的装载费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是只有单方受益的霸王交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我具体内容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这台人形机器人太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动 到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 去搬下一箱货物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到刚刚那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 移动到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说不要飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这人形机器人不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙听得懂你之外的人说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的话他也会听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据军纪 在允许范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可移交命令权
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 我有个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快递哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在干活在干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让破废铁干活 自己却在一边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大蠢材 果然还是应该把他丢进海里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可能只是在休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法从贵官的行动中发现意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是集中精神的一种手段罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这么热的天 亏他们还能这么好动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有纪律 他们的教官在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测 儿童的训练没有教官参与
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要如何将他们培养成社会的一员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请下达下一个命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好诈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞到天上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务执行出现障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请批准排除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要对他们造成伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 状态怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命 中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？你在做什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道还做啊 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议的材料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亚斯 指甲 这颗星球 上 没有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的 话 就 送给 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 我们边走边聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有好礼物可以送给弟弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟 弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手很巧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何谓「弟弟」？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「弟弟」…就是兄弟的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比自己小的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家 人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旧社会中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于雌雄配偶及血缘关系而构成的社会单位的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有过这样的习俗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德没有家人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低 效率 不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低效率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得雷德住的地方很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝贝尔好像想问你关于宇宙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙 的 事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他对天体啦 还有能飞向宇宙的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他身体很虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无法自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身 体 虚弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的胸部有点疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银河同盟中 体弱的人类将会被淘汰及处分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法参加战斗的人是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用…怎么能这样 雷德你无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不 懂 你 的提 问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:08:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能从与那个人的对话中得到有意义的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 就去见见奥尔德姆医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔 德姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个医生 不过大家都称他为贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是加尔刚蒂亚里知识最渊博的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 奥尔德姆医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生 艾米来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我带了客人来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道就是雷德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说有事想问问医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我还有工作没有做完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 一会儿我会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面等着我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方希望你提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是听到过传言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是能理解语言的机械所发出的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这项技术已经失传了 没想到能亲眼看到实物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 可以 提问 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能回答得上 你就尽管问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请教如何才能回到银河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 以我的知识无法回答你的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 大部分古老的智慧都已失传
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是行星穿梭技术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们目前所保留的关于天空的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它应该不是你所要找寻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 帮不上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 也没 办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 可以再 问 一个 问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听听你对这个舰团组织的见解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓见解是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰团非常没有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令体系以及军事训练也不完善
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的行动也毫无秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解保护弱者的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星来客是这样看的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所指的效率似乎相当狭义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不妨去见见贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能从与那个人的对话中得到有意义的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有意义应该由你自己判断
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PartB
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 医生也不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝贝尔 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}欢迎回来 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人就是雷德哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是姐姐的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次 见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是艾米的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也说想见见贝贝尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方希望你提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那个 难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这就是Chamber的通信机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 真的会说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Chamber先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机是用于支援驾驶员的人工智能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷 地球的语言也能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人手不够了 你快来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 帅哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我得去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得现在气氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么气氛正好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说不是你想的那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 贝贝尔 雷德就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太急了 小心摔倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 姐姐总是匆匆忙忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥 你真的是从宇宙来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的生活是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河同盟的主要任务是与希迪亚斯进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亚斯是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁人类生存的异种生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一直在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从银河同盟创立至今 战斗从未停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这里的生活完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪消耗者唯有死亡一途
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 真的很艰辛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你习惯这里的生活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法理解加尔刚蒂亚的组织构造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请解释低效及无意义经营的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团不是组织啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家聚在一起罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时而吵架 时而互帮互助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这样的方式活下去罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问意义何在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能安心地活着不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此回答感到不解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的行动目的应该是讨伐敌人希迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则人类无法获得稳定的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:16:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银河同盟中 你这样的人类会立刻被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淘汰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果将希迪亚斯全部都消灭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河同盟会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥你会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到下一道命令之前待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 如果没有下一道命令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有继续待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我们一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为待命不就是指一直活下去的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你的人形机器人被乔给抢走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得当了次英雄 现在却不成样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道自己的行动是否有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是帮我们赶走海贼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我只是在监视Chamber而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是还没适应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法判断我应该采取什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该采取的行动啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放弃你那军人思维怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放 弃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 更加自由地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集雨水！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是气象现象 没有毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生紧急事态了 用你的人形机器人来收集雨水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡水可是很珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有帆布 把它展开来收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 就这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵官的脑波产生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在意友军的战况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在目前状况下 贵官的思考毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总觉得他好可怜…一个人流落到陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个帅哥没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你很担心他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你湿透了呢 会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家把身体擦干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的骤雨很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次观测到集中降雨现象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中也会下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的病人也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我并不认为自己是不被需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 还有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾 米？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥也是一直被别人所需要才能活到现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有对战斗有益的人才需要存活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 反向思考一下 对雷德哥哥来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有你觉得需要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐 彼此都需要对方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 我需要我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对同盟而言 无意义者没有生存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这对你来说是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听姐姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道这是什么 却在制作着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是笛子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中完全不需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛 子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 它可以发出声音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥？你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是 我也不 知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是想起什么悲伤的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你 把它 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是纱雅推荐的 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 还是无法定位坐标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测情报不足 仍需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还需要进一步了解这个星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要 贵官早晚将与主力部队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道的

